data.description: Welcome to your own piece of paradise; enter the private gate, down the extended drive to the serene setting! This exquisite home is nestled on over 2.5 acres of flat land, offering a perfect blend of luxury & nature. The stunning residence boasts ample space for everyone, w/spacious rooms & modern finishes throughout. Remodeled Kitchen features a pantry, SS appliances, fireplace & oversized windows. Step outside to your private oasis, complete with a refreshing Doughboy pool & expansive deck perfect for entertaining. Enjoy cozy evenings by the firepit, BBQs on the patio, visit your animals in the 2 Stall Barn. Surrounded by breathtaking natural beauty, imagine all of the memories to be made here! Live your dream – schedule a viewing today!
